steps.name: Given the user is on the ZigWheels
When the user clicks on the Login/Signup
Then the user clicks on the Apple login option
And user provide Phone Number in Apple login page
And user enter the incorrect password in Apple login page
Then display a invalid errorMessage in Apple login page
And the user closes the Apple login page
